{"tid":548408,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★對沖基金經理預測 Bitcoin 2018年底見4萬美元！","createTime":"2018-02-02T13:36:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-02T13:46:38.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d7e5f68f5a5634356a333bc78ca5dad0295389eb","tid":548408,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T13:36:21.000Z","msg":"虛擬貨幣比特幣（Bitcoin）升勢持續，有投資者擔心Bitcoin起泡，亦有Bitcoin大好友繼續唱好，並大膽預測明年可望升至40,000美元。<br />\n<br />\n美國Galaxy investment主管、<span style=\"color: red;\">對沖基金Fortress前基金經理Michael Novogratz預測，Bitcoin兌美元價格2018年底可望升至40,000美元，</span>較今日高位9891.62美元升逾4倍。他又估計以太幣將會升至500美元，或從現價升逾3倍。Michael Novogratz也預計虛擬貨幣合計市值明年進一步擴大至2萬億美元。<br />\nMichael Novogratz看好Bitcoin前景，正迎來一股資金大浪潮，不只是美國，而是全球市場。他計劃成立規模達5億美元的數碼資產基金。對虛擬貨幣價格異常波動，Michael Novogratz指虛擬貨幣跟商品不同之處，是虛擬貨幣不像商品具備有效的供應反應（supply response）。比特幣不能增加發行量，上限為2,100萬個，因此比特幣成投機者天堂，亦令虛擬貨幣價格波動性放大，所以每次升勢又急又顯著，下跌時又會急跌50%。<br />\n另一位虛擬貨幣大好友Fundstrat創辦人Tom Lee則調高比特幣2018年中目標價，由6,000美元上調至11,500美元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20171128/57515253\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171128%2F57515253&d=0QNKk0%2FbSnXi%2BtqAxhkz9vM6KyiA14vjm6WlJCMZo68%3D&h=ae9ea615\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171128%2F57515253&h=c0576e8a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20171128/57515253</a>"},{"pid":"93e5b1855639285974f215b72945d05bc7d8b657","tid":548408,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T13:36:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29ade9802ed31890905511f7ea4c1a5acfc36b55","tid":548408,"uid":19557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T13:38:04.000Z","msg":"對沖基金經理仲唔快d成副身家入貨"},{"pid":"4b8c0194c28d03d1f580f430b33